## Configuration

### Environment Variables

Configure the app using environment variables:

```bash
# Development
flutter run --dart-define=MIZU_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Production
flutter run --release --dart-define=MIZU_BASE_URL=https://api.example.com
```

### Android Emulator

For Android emulator, use `10.0.2.2` to access host machine's localhost:
```bash
flutter run --dart-define=MIZU_BASE_URL=http://10.0.2.2:3000
```

